{"tid":1889756,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"17年前既今日，沙士傳入香港","createTime":"2020-02-20T19:06:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-21T04:00:42.000Z","uid":69231,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"db096a770c6daf92a92e7997e2b7c00b22b33023","tid":1889756,"uid":69231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T19:06:55.000Z","msg":"2003年2月21日，劉劍倫將病毒帶入香港。廣州中山大學附屬第二醫院（中山二院）的64歲退休教授劉劍倫，在2月11-13日於中山二院工作時接觸過數名非典型肺炎病人受到傳染，其後被發現出現肺炎病徵，例如他在2月17日於廣州照的X光片顯示肺部左下區域有霧化。但已染肺炎的劉劍倫並未有隔離就醫，他只是自行服用抗生素，更於2月21日攜同妻子到香港，入住京華酒店911號房一晚。"},{"pid":"8e7e8eaa9b1fa69b5a09bd244d151c54a42c41f7","tid":1889756,"uid":69231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T19:07:29.000Z","msg":"from wiki"},{"pid":"8481d037ce7e77a2660207a269462faa664c6f82","tid":1889756,"uid":69231,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T19:09:45.000Z","msg":"17年後又再重演<br />\n只係仲早左個幾月爆發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f978a04bbbb3a386c454da97bbf0aff6a02570dc","tid":1889756,"uid":167721,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T19:10:17.000Z","msg":"小弟個時冇中沙士但肺炎入咗院<br />\n諗返起都<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申：幼稚園 記得零碎片段"},{"pid":"d81a96e6fc3b4dae2c3242ff49733c9ffe769eb8","tid":1889756,"uid":95761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f978a04bbbb3a386c454da97bbf0aff6a02570dc","tid":1889756,"uid":167721,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T19:10:17.000Z","msg":"小弟個時冇中沙士但肺炎入咗院<br />\n諗返起都<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申：幼稚園 記得零碎片段"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T19:12:25.000Z","msg":"幼稚園嗰陣肺炎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"646e6055b06abef9b551a7f06693e9006af5f154","tid":1889756,"uid":69231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T19:13:36.000Z","msg":"咁驚 有無以為為你都染左沙士<br />\n<br />\n我個陣都係讀緊幼稚